('Growth Mindset', 'Believing you can improve', 'lifeskills', 7, 22, '# Growth Mindset\n\n**Fixed:** "I''m not good at this"\n**Growth:** "I''m not good at this YET"\n\n**Key ideas:**\n- Effort leads to mastery\n- Mistakes are learning\n- Challenges help you grow', 22, true, '[{"question":"Growth mindset says...","options":["You can not change","Effort leads to growth","Give up easily","Avoid challenges"],"correct":1}]'),
('Online Safety', 'Staying safe online', 'lifeskills', 7, 22, '# Digital Safety\n\n**Protect:**\n- Personal information\n- Passwords (strong, unique)\n- Your reputation\n\n**Watch for:**\n- Phishing scams\n- Cyberbullying\n- Inappropriate content\n\nThink before you click!', 22, true, '[{"question":"Passwords should be...","options":["Simple","Same for all sites","Strong and unique","Your birthday"],"correct":2}]'),
('Career Exploration', 'Planning your future', 'lifeskills', 7, 25, '# Exploring Careers\n\n**Steps:**\n1. Identify interests and skills\n2. Research career options\n3. Talk to professionals\n4. Consider education needed\n5. Set goals\n\nIt''s okay to change your mind!', 25, true, '[{"question":"First step in career exploration?","options":["Get a job","Identify interests","Apply to college","Quit school"],"correct":1}]');